## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="820eb-104">属性或字段必须是公共的。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="820eb-104">The property or field must be public.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="820eb-105">包含属性的类必须标记有<xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.ManagementEntityAttribute>属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="820eb-105">The class that contains the property must be marked with the <xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.ManagementEntityAttribute> attribute.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="820eb-106">未检测的任何字段或类中未标有这个或另一个 WMI 提供程序扩展属性的属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="820eb-106">Any fields or properties in the class that are not marked with this or another WMI Provider Extensions attribute will not be instrumented.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="820eb-107">下面的示例演示如何使用 ManagementConfiguration 特性标记某个属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="820eb-107">The following example shows how to use the ManagementConfiguration attribute to mark a property.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="820eb-108">此属性向 WMI 公开。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="820eb-108">This property is exposed to WMI.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
// Use the ManagementConfiguration attribute to specify that a property  
// is a read/write property in the provider. Consumers will be  
// able to get and set this property value through WMI.  
[ManagementConfiguration]  
public double ReadableWritableProperty  
{  
    get { return this.propertyValue; }  
    set { this.propertyValue = value; }  
}  
```
